rom the rails draw before closing late to finish fifth over 1800m at Kyoto Dirt last start. Outsprinted in the run home but kept coming and looks suited by the extra ground. Won only try course and distance. Can do much better. 9. ONE PUTT worked home well and finished second last time over 2100m at Tokyo Dirt when resuming from a spell, beaten 3 lengths. The engagement of Keisuke Dazai is a positive move. Likely improver with strong prospects.\",\"runners\":[2,13,10,9],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Japan Tips","tipRunnerNumbers":[2,10,13,3]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,3,10]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,2,10,13]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[13,2,7,10]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[10,13,8,2]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[13,10,8,2]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,5,10,6]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[10,2,13,3]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":12,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":12,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":12,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":12,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":12,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":12,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":12,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"DailyDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":10,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":9,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Treble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":10,"venueMnemonic":"HAN","raceType":"R"}}]}}}